info.+content: Go! プリンセスプリキュア

Haruka Haruno has dreamed of being a princess since she was a little girl. As a middle schooler, she goes to the boarding school Noble Academy, where she meets two royal fairies from Hope Kingdom. Together with her friends, she becomes a Princess Pretty Cure in order to save Hope Kingdom and protect people's dreams from the Witch of Despair and her minions.
#1: "Miracle Go! Princess Precure" (Miracle Gо！プリンセスプリキュア) by Karin Isobe
